<div class="fs-4">
  <h1 class="mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

	<p>
	  <strong>
		  Why did you create this app?
		</strong>
		<br>
		We're fathers just like you who wanted a space for dads to connect and share
		what we go through on the daily. There's so much to build and we're just
		getting started!
	</p>

	<p>
	  <strong>
		  How do I make a post?
		</strong>
		<br>
		Go to the "üè† Home" page and at the top you'll see a section with a default
		question shown. Underneath it is a big input field &mdash; type what you
		want to post and then hit the "Share" button.
	</p>

	<p>
	  <strong>
		  How do I reply to comments made by other dads?
		</strong>
		<br>
		Whenever anyone makes a comment, you'll see an input field with the
		placeholder text of "Reply to NAME", where NAME is who made the comment.
		Type what you want to share and hit the enter key.
	</p>

	<p>
	  <strong>
		  How do I answer the Question of the Day?
		</strong>
		<br>
		Go to the "üè† Home" page and at the top you'll see a section with a default
		question shown. Underneath it is a link which says "Question of the Day".
		Click it and the question of the day will appear. Type what you want to post
		and then hit the "Share" button.
	</p>

